org.apache.tephra.metrics

Class DefaultMetricsCollector

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.common.util.concurrent.AbstractIdleService
      • org.apache.tephra.metrics.TxMetricsCollector
        • org.apache.tephra.metrics.DefaultMetricsCollector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.google.common.util.concurrent.Service, MetricsCollector

    public class DefaultMetricsCollector
extends TxMetricsCollector
    Default metrics collector implementation using Yammer Metrics.

    The reporting frequency for this collector can be configured by setting the data.tx.metrics.period configuration property to the reporting frequency in seconds.
